node_modules
dist-ssr
*.local

# NOTE: dist/ is intentionally NOT ignored here.
# The built SPA in dist/ is shipped as package-data so that
# `pip install .` / `pip install git+https://...` gives users a working
# `focustracer gui` without needing Node/npm installed. Rebuild with
# `npm run build` and commit the result before tagging a release.

